Satya Golla and Steve Simon

Created 2022-03-21

Find community ids

cd                                     %>%
  tibble                               %>%
  distinct(cd_id)                      %>%
  arrange(cd_id)                       %>%
  pull(cd_id)                           -> cd_list
county_plot <- function(co, cd, i) {
  cd %<>% filter(cd_id==i)
  ggplot(co, aes())                     +
    geom_sf(
      fill=NA,
      color="darkred")                  +
    ggtitle(cd$cd_name)                 +
    geom_sf(
      data=cd,
      aes(),
      fill="white",
      color="darkgreen")                -> plot_co
  plot(plot_co)
}

extract_bg <- function(bl_counts, i) {
  bl_counts                            %>%
    tibble                             %>%
    filter(cd_id==i)                   %>%
    distinct(bg_id)                    %>%
    arrange(bg_id)                     %>%
    pull(bg_id)                       
}

extract_bl <- function(bl_list, j) {
  bl_list                              %>%
    tibble                             %>%
    filter(bg_id==j)                   %>%
    distinct(bl_id)                    %>%
    arrange(bl_id)                     %>%
    pull(bl_id)                       
}

bg_plot <- function(cd, i, bg, bg_counts, j) {
  ti <- j
  cd_i <- filter(cd, cd_id==i)
  bg_j <- filter(bg, bg_id==j)
  bg_counts                            %>%
    filter(cd_id==i)                   %>%
    filter(bg_id==j)                   %>%
    print
  ggplot(cd_i, aes())                   +
    geom_sf(
      fill="lightgreen",
      color="darkgreen")                +
    geom_sf(
      data=bg_j,
      aes(),
      fill=NA,
      color="darkred")                  +
    ggtitle(ti)                         -> plot_bg
  plot(plot_bg)
}

display_blocks <- function(bl_counts, i, j) {
  bl                                   %>%
    mutate(
      bg_id=str_sub(bl_id, 1, 12))     %>%
    filter(bg_id==j)                   %>%
    pull(bl_id)                         -> bl_list_j
  bl_list_j                            %>%
    length                             %>%
    paste0(" blocks in bg")            %>%
    print
  bl_counts                            %>%
    filter(cd_id==i)                   %>%
    pull(bl_id)                         -> cd_list_i
  setdiff(bl_list_j, cd_list_i)        %>%
    length                             %>%
    paste0(" blocks outside cd")       %>%
    print
  bl_counts                            %>%
    filter(cd_id==i)                   %>%
    filter(bg_id==j)                   %>%
    select(
      bl_id,
      prop_in,
      people_in,
      units_in)                        %>%
    data.frame                         %>%
    print
}

ti <- paste0( s3\(bg_id, ", ", s3\)people_in, /, s3\(people, ", ", s3\)housing_units_in, /, s3$housing_units)

for (i in cd_list[1]) {
  county_plot(co, cd, i)
  bg_list <- extract_bg(bl_counts, i)
  for (j in bg_list) {
    display_blocks(bl_counts, i, j)
    bg_plot(cd, i, bg, bg_counts, j)
  }
}
